## ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Phase 1: Kritik Güvenlik (1-2 hafta)
1. API key vault entegrasyonu
2. Session token encryption
3. Real key derivation (Argon2)
4. HSM integration stub

### Phase 2: Kanal Entegrasyonları (2-3 hafta)
1. Telegram (teloxide güncel API)
2. Discord (serenity güncel API)
3. Slack (slack-api güncel)
4. Webhook (HTTP POST)

### Phase 3: Voice & Skills (1-2 hafta)
1. Whisper STT (whisper-rs)
2. Wake word detection
3. Skill LLM integration
4. Marketplace packaging

### Phase 4: Enterprise (1-2 hafta)
1. SSO OAuth2 flow
2. RBAC implementation
3. Tenant isolation

### Phase 5: Test & Docs (1 hafta)
1. Benchmark implementations
2. API documentation
3. Getting started guide
